original_title: NPP leads 10 more polling divisions including Dambulla, Vavuniya, Chilaw
original_body_lines: The National People’s Power (NPP) has secured victories in the Dambulla, Vavuniya, Anuradhapura-East, Dedigama, Chilaw, Maskeliya, Yapahuwa, Yatinuwara, Deraniyagala and Bingiriya polling divisions.
